			-Profile icon, linked to Profile
			-Search Bar, linked to Search Results

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Home Page:		-Navgiation bar
			-Activity feed	
				>Posts from subscribed Discussions
				>Create post:
					>>Select discussion
					>>Add contents
					>>Mark as spoiler
					>>Post
			
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Profile Page:		-Navgiation bar
			-Avatar
			-Username
			-Name
			-Short bio
			-Watch-list
			-Settings
			-Friends list
			-Customize (Edit mode) <--create a seperate frame in Balsamiq for edit mode
				>Change Avatar
				>Change Theme
				>Privacy settings
			-Logout

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Friends:		-Nav bar
			-Friends of the user (each friend linked to their Profile page)


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Search Results:		-Navgiation bar
			-Results:
				>Title, linked to Series
				>Brief description
	
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Series Page:		-Navgiation bar
			-Title
			-Embedded image or video, linked to a trailer
			-Plot overview
			-Ratings and reviews
			-Cast
			-Top 3 or 4 discussions, linked to a Subthread page
			-Add to watch-list

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Discussions Page:	-Navigation bar
			-Threads/posts, in chronological order; each linked to a Subthread page
				>if  TV series, threads are organized by season
			-Create a new post
				>if a TV series, user must select which season they are posting about from a dropdown list
			-View Comments button, linked to Subthread page
		
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Subthread Page:		-Navigation bar
			-Comments/Replies
			-Like/Dislike post or comments
			-Leave a comment
			-Post comment
